      "source_index": 1,
      "target_index": 3,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "‘洗涤’含义扩展为‘浸润、浸湿’。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 1,
      "target_index": 4,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "‘洗’引申指液体溅洒之意，后常通‘濺’。"
